{"tid":1367209,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都可以係連儂牆(忽發其想)","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T10:37:13.000Z","uid":290410,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03bb58a4e5b71e761518ad8c9b5f94c7a8fd3601","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"今次想發起一個活動就係戴住頭盔去搭港鐵去元朗，表示警黑勾結造成搭港鐵都要戴頭盔，希望依個只係一個起點但當出街人人都戴既時間依家就係一個好大既保護傘，頭盔唔會畀人用頭盔做一個指控證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n1 扭轉社會既負面形象，係因為警方唔能夠保護市民，所以出街要戴頭盔保護自己，戴頭盔唔再係被標籤示威者，唔再係被標籤佢地所謂既搞事。<br />\n2 依場革命我地要增加多啲「小動作」融入日常，有冇活動都可以戴，例如大家見面要講光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n3 既然不合作運動係依一刻行唔通，就要退一步先搞按章工作由小運動做起。<br />\n<br />\n初頭都覺得連儂牆係好小既事，係大家集體打飛機，但係經過一個月左右慢慢睇到啲成效，例如:銀髮族遊行，其實係可以慢慢感染到身邊既人，起碼都知有好多同路人，即使佢地冇出到黎。依個係一個拋磚引玉，唔需要局限連儂牆既地點形式，連儂牆係一個信念。認同請推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04f299424bc89d27767d192773f05c0eb7c3249","tid":1367209,"uid":259700,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e35d9973cce53f232674c3fc97522e491133379","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ec5e1f96639404dbbbd87badb5ed012a2eb473","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04f299424bc89d27767d192773f05c0eb7c3249","tid":1367209,"uid":259700,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"抛磚引玉，唔想大家畀任何形式限制住自己思想。但用memo痴係身好容易甩可以用其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n大家可能覺得戴安全帽依件事好戇鳩件事好少，但係一方面可能減低物料組既運輸成本，每次都要傳頭盔口罩，如果每個人都有物料前線既壓力就會少好多。二係點解啲手足唔帶走物料係因為驚被狗用依樣野黎入佢地。所以打開左依個關口以後條路相信可以好行啲"},{"pid":"5d7df860e0edec1099ddda47deadb1246e59e81a","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6fdfd0c46bdb2f1090d6b4d399b659483134a1","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1216287411cc2f0bfd1fd2d8e654ca53a5d16fb0","tid":1367209,"uid":148524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"痴memo紙係頭盔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86725a151e5db9c96e9d663e6cfef4450e660fd0","tid":1367209,"uid":13908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b-YHgb5V5hU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb-YHgb5V5hU&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=b2f51dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b-YHgb5V5hU</a>"},{"pid":"60192fd5bedd70f9614076392454536e25cb05ff","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86725a151e5db9c96e9d663e6cfef4450e660fd0","tid":1367209,"uid":13908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b-YHgb5V5hU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb-YHgb5V5hU&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=b2f51dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b-YHgb5V5hU</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc721041418daba144cc7b9fd188e9649377364","tid":1367209,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:37